            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">心水序言里一句话：史记里除了姓名是真什么都是假的，小说里除了姓名是假什么都是真的，沉重的话题，沉重的历史</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="507743012">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-507743012" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-507743012" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="507743012">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/geekinmedia/">宋燕</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2012-03-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">好多年以前读过。作者是我同事，多年来所有的闲暇时间都泡在档案馆，这本书就是他的泡档案馆成果。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

<div id="comments" class="comment-list new noshow">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1183013793">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1183013793" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1183013793" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1183013793">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
